description:
Contents:
- Citizen's Country Wear "A casual outfit designed to look like the clothes worn by an agricultural worker."
- Citizen's Kid's Country "A casual outfit for kids designed to look like the clothes worn by an agricultural worker."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Clothing Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
- Flower Hat: White	 "A straw hat decorated with breezy blue flowers."
- Small Flower Hat: White "A small straw hat decorated with breezy blue flowers."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Fashion Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
name: Citizen's Country Wear Set
